Description: CTS has specialized in delivering sophisticated technology-based training solutions to government & commercial clients on time & on budget.
Headquarters Regions: East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: CTS has specialized in delivering sophisticated technology-based training solutions to both government and commercial clients on time and on budget. The company's line of business includes providing management consulting services. CTS uses virtual environments that mimic on-the-job training for both stages. Trainees are given knowledge then immediately asked to apply that knowledge to a task or situation in the virtual environment. The application of the knowledge often requires hazard recognition and decision-making skills to complete. Computer-based training simulations offer a first-person perspective similar to that used in many video games and allow trainees to observe, experience and interact with a world similar to the one in which they will be working. The virtual training environment provides learners with a context for what they are learning and contributes to higher retention and better understanding. With this approach, CTS helps companies improve safety and decrease the total cost of training. The training modules also have the unique ability to capture behavioral data that can help predict a trainee's probability of being involved in an accident. Custom-built and off-the-shelf courses address a variety of safety and operations needs -- from basic tasks to 3D simulation of heavy equipment operation and complex emergency scenarios.

Description: iShopWiser is a shopping application that helps consumers makes wiser shopping decisions.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Boston Area, East Coast, New England
Full Description: iShopWiser is a social shopping community offering visual suggestions to users shopping questions. The inspiration behind this new initiative is quite simple, as exemplified by the tagline: "Just show me the suggestion". Save me time searching through comments and recommendations and just post visual suggestions under my requests; the exact picture and link of the product being suggested. How many times you feel that you know what your need is, but don't know what specific product or model you should buy? Like me you might have been in a situation where you know that you need a backpack or camera, but what model or brand to pick, you've no idea. So like most of us you either google or go to review sites to read all the comments and recommendations left by other users. You can search through page after page hoping for that golden suggestion. Full Description: Luxe is a start-up luxury rental property company. We are looking to fund our first acquisition: 15 villas at The Trump Founders Residences in Rio Grande, Puerto Rico. We are seeking $135,000  in short term funding. We have a lender for the $13.5 million to purchase the villas, decorate & outfit them luxuriously  but need $135,000 to allow for payment of the property visit, trips to and from Puerto Rico for the closing, and other up-front expenses. We will repay loan in 90 days. Luxe is going after medical tourism as well as traditional vacationers as guests. We will offer a Land Rover LR4 with each villa. No need to rent a car while staying with us. Also, if the guest so desires, for an additional fee of $8-10,000 per week, they can lease our brand new 2013 Audi R8 if they want to drive something more exotic! Guests will have complete access to the 36-hole Trump International Golf Course & Club House, a golf cart, our own private beach and all of the amenities of the Grand Melia, Puerto Rico--a gorgeous open-air concept, 5-Star resort...including their amazing restaurants, largest lagoon pool in the Caribbean, YHI Spa and so much more!  The properties are brand new construction, and discounted approximately by half. It's the financial opportunity of a lifetime for our first acquisition! Situated at the foothills of the El Yunque Rainforest--the only rainforest in the US Forest System, the Trump Founders residences sit on the Trump International Golf Course to the south and the Atlantic Ocean to the north. Simply gorgeous!  The tax incentives put in place by Puerto Rican Act 20/22 are further incentivizing US residents, such as ourselves to relocate. With 0% Federal Income Tax and 0% Capital Gains until 2035, Puerto Rico is becoming a very attractive island for US mainland professionals.

Full Description: GreekPull is an online platform that allows current or alumni members of fraternities, sororities and other on-campus fraternal groups to create and fund projects that support themselves or their local chapter. Whether it’s a service project, an expansion project for the group’s facility or a special event, GreekPull helps coordinate funding from a broad range of donors. The process is simple and transparent – local chapter members and alumni are able to create campaigns on the site, and alumni, friends and others can use GreekPull to help fund the project. Incentives can be given for donations as well, and donors are able to track the progress of each campaign as it raises funds. GreekPull has been featured as one of Louisville’s rising start-ups in Insider Louisville News, a guest on Louisville start-up radio, as well as an invited speaker at the Professional Fraternity Association National Conference. On July 22nd 2013, GreekPull was officially recognized as an Associate Member of the Professional Fraternity Association.
